reviewText: Not for a first timer. She does eg..., no I'm not going to say that....she does great work. Not much information but I liked watching her technique.
Ostrich Egg Carving needs to be more detailed. Video is good quality .Would like to see more of this work to get a better feel for carving.
very poor quality video that is very hard to watch. I would not recommend this to anyone who is a first time carver as they would probably become very discouraged with the idea of egg carving.

Great teacher but poor camera work. Not for beginning egg carvers. Knowing what I know now I would rather have bought the DVD or not at all. After download it keeps stopping and you must start all over again. If you have experence carving eggs & want to learn from one of the best carvers around order the DVD not the download. Save your money.
